OL,4,CPatrick Devine's murder
OL,6,FA reward of up to #20,000 is being
OL,7,Foffered for information on the
OL,8,F"ruthless" murder of Patrick Devine 20
OL,9,Fyears ago.
OL,11,FThe 51-year-old sheep farmer and part-
OL,12,Ftime nurse was found shot dead in his
OL,13,Fhome on the Mullintill Road in Claudy,
OL,14,FCo Londonderry, on September 13 2004.
OL,16,FHe was shot several times in the head
OL,17,Fand chest as he was eating a meal.
