OL,6,FDespite extensive police inquiries and
OL,7,Fthe arrest of five people during the
OL,8,Finvestigation, no one has been held
OL,9,Faccountable for his murder.
OL,11,FDetectives have issued a renewed
OL,12,Fappeal on the 20th anniversary of his
OL,13,Fdeath, backed by a reward of up to
OL,14,F#20,000 from the charity Crimestoppers.
