OL,3,CFresh appeal for information on
OL,4,CPatrick Devine's murder
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark Gibson
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is now 20 years since
OL,8,FPatrick's life was taken from him in a
OL,9,Fbrutal and calculated manner, and his
OL,10,Ffamily's wait for justice has gone on
OL,11,Ffor far too long."Mr Devine was well
OL,12,Fknown in the area, especially for his
OL,13,Ffarming activities, and also for his
OL,14,Fwork as a nurse. We believe that some
OL,15,Fpeople resented his success.
