OL,6,F"It is still the view of police that
OL,7,FPatrick was the victim of a contract
OL,8,Fkilling carried out by an organised
OL,9,Fcrime group with paramilitary links
OL,10,Fagainst a background of rumours of
OL,11,Falleged sheep stealing and land
OL,12,Fdisputes, although Mr Devine himself
OL,13,Fhad a clear criminal record.
