OL,4,CPatrick Devine's murder
OL,6,F"On this, the 20th anniversary of his
OL,7,Fmurder, we are appealing to the
OL,8,Fcommunity for their assistance and
OL,9,Fhelp."I am asking people to think
OL,10,Fabout what happened to Patrick 20
OL,11,Fyears ago and the brutal circumstances
OL,12,Fof his death ` he was shot several
OL,13,Ftimes in the head and chest as he was
OL,14,Fhaving a meal in his home.
