OL,3,CFresh appeal for information on
OL,4,CPatrick Devine's murder
OL,6,F"The individuals who did this are
OL,7,Fdangerous, ruthless and,
OL,8,Funfortunately, have never been held
OL,9,Faccountable. I am appealing to anyone
OL,10,Fwho knows anything about Patrick's
OL,11,Fmurder to come forward, talk to us and
OL,12,Fhelp us end the pain which his family
OL,13,Fhas endured for all these years.
OL,15,F"In the 20 years since Patrick's
OL,16,Fmurder, circumstances and allegiances
OL,17,Fmay have changed. If anyone now feels
OL,18,Fthey are able to talk to us, we are
OL,19,Fhere and ready to listen, and you can
OL,20,Fcontact us on 101.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
